          disable user access, configure integrations, manage deployments, and act on behalf of the
          organization within the Service.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section class="mb-8">
        <h2 class="mb-4">4. Acceptable Use and Restrictions</h2>
        <p class="mb-4">
